track_notes:
Warning: Alpine route over glaciers and rock ridges via Jubilaeumgsgrat to northern and then southern summit Wildspitze. Snow and mixed climb to summit. Way down with short UIAA II climb section.
We did the tour with a mountainguide in a group of 6. 
5 hours to summit with 11 hours in total needed to reach Taschachhaus.

Barely any space on summit for wire antennas. With good wx expect lot of climbers.
track_title: Alpine high tour to Wildspitze and onward to Taschachhaus
